{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium "Recent Delivery Jobs" Shopify section for a local furniture delivery and removalist business.
    
    This section must dynamically display the Page metafield:
    
    custom.recent_jobs
    
    This metafield is a List of Recent Job Metaobject References.
    
    Each Recent Job contains:
    
    • Job Title
    • Pickup Suburb
    • Drop-off Suburb
    • Item Type
    • Service Type
    • Image
    • Job Date
    • Customer Rating
    • Short Description
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    SECTION HEADER
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Heading:
    
    Recent Furniture Deliveries Near You
    
    Subheading:
    
    Browse some of our recently completed furniture deliveries across Sydney. Every delivery shown below was completed by Titan Express using our oversized van and professional furniture handling equipment.
    
    Add a subtle animated underline beneath the heading.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    CARD DESIGN
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Create premium modern cards.
    
    Use:
    
    • White glossy background
    • Rounded corners (18-20px)
    • Soft shadows
    • Modern spacing
    • Premium typography
    • Mobile first design
    • SVG icons only
    • Smooth hover animation
    • Slight card lift on hover
    • Image zoom effect on hover
    
    Desktop
    
    3 cards per row
    
    Tablet
    
    2 cards
    
    Mobile
    
    Horizontal swipe carousel
    
    Lazy load all images.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    CARD LAYOUT
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    TOP
    
    Large featured image
    
    Rounded corners
    
    Image ratio 16:9
    
    Lazy loaded
    
    Middle
    
    Display
    
    Job Title
    
    Large Bold
    
    Underneath display
    
    📍 Pickup Suburb
    
    ↓
    
    🚚 Titan Express
    
    ↓
    
    📍 Delivery Suburb
    
    Make the route visually attractive using modern SVG timeline icons.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    JOB DETAILS
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Display as premium information chips
    
    📦 Item Type
    
    🚚 Service Type
    
    📅 Job Date
    
    ⭐ Customer Rating
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    DESCRIPTION
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Display the Short Description below the information chips.
    
    Limit to approximately three lines.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    TRUST BADGES
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Display premium badges automatically on every card.
    
    ✓ Oversized Van
    
    ✓ Furniture Protected
    
    ✓ Professional Equipment
    
    ✓ Same Day Available
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    BOTTOM CTA
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Display button
    
    Get Similar Delivery Quote
    
    Button should smoothly scroll to the Quote Form.
    
    Use configurable Quote Form ID.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    OPTIONAL MODAL
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    When clicking the card, open a premium popup.
    
    Popup displays
    
    Large Image
    
    Job Title
    
    Pickup Suburb
    
    Drop-off Suburb
    
    Item Type
    
    Service Type
    
    Customer Rating
    
    Job Date
    
    Full Description
    
    Bottom CTA
    
    Get My Quote
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    EMPTY STATE
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    If no Recent Jobs are assigned to the page
    
    Hide the entire section automatically.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    SEO
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Use semantic HTML.
    
    Section
    
    <header>
    
    Heading
    
    <h2>
    
    Each Job
    
    <article>
    
    Pickup and Delivery suburbs should use semantic text.
    
    Images require descriptive ALT text generated dynamically such as:
    
    "Sofa delivery from Parramatta to Strathfield by Titan Express"
    
    Lazy load images.
    
    Avoid CLS.
    
    Optimize Core Web Vitals.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    ACCESSIBILITY
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Keyboard accessible
    
    ARIA labels
    
    High colour contrast
    
    Screen reader friendly
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    SCHEMA
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    If Recent Jobs exist,
    
    generate ItemList schema dynamically.
    
    Each Recent Job becomes a ListItem.
    
    Include
    
    Job Title
    
    Description
    
    Image
    
    Date
    
    Service Area
    
    Do not generate duplicate schema.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    PERFORMANCE
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    No external libraries.
    
    No jQuery.
    
    Pure Shopify Liquid
    
    CSS
    
    JavaScript
    
    Optimize for Lighthouse 95+
    
    Use CSS variables.
    
    Lazy load images.
    
    Load JavaScript only when this section exists.
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    CUSTOMIZATION
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    Allow merchant to customize:
    
    Section Heading
    
    Subheading
    
    Background colour
    
    Card colour
    
    Card radius
    
    Card shadow
    
    Cards per row
    
    Enable carousel
    
    Enable popup
    
    Enable trust badges
    
    Enable quote button
    
    Quote Form ID
    
    Animation speed
    
    Spacing
    
    Section padding
    
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    FINAL GOAL
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    
    The section should feel like a premium portfolio of real furniture deliveries rather than a product grid.
    
    It should increase customer trust, improve local SEO, encourage quote requests, and showcase real work completed by Titan Express across Sydney.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}
{% assign recent_jobs = page.metafields.custom.recent_jobs.value %}

{% if recent_jobs.size > 0 %}
  {% style %}
    .ai-recent-jobs-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
      background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -8px;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{ block.settings.heading_color }}, transparent);
      animation: ai-underline-{{ ai_gen_id }} 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes ai-underline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      0%, 100% { transform: scaleX(0.3); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: scaleX(1); opacity: 1; }
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
      color: {{ block.settings.subheading_color }};
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.cards_per_row }}, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 989px) {
      .ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 24px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 749px) {
      .ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        {% if block.settings.enable_mobile_carousel %}
          display: flex;
          overflow-x: auto;
          scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
          gap: 16px;
          padding-bottom: 16px;
          -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
        {% else %}
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 20px;
        {% endif %}
      }

      {% if block.settings.enable_mobile_carousel %}
        .ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar {
          height: 6px;
        }

        .ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
          background: #f1f1f1;
          border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
          background: #888;
          border-radius: 10px;
        }
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      background: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
      border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_radius }}px;
      box-shadow: {{ block.settings.card_shadow }};
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease, box-shadow {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
      cursor: {% if block.settings.enable_popup %}pointer{% else %}default{% endif %};
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    @media (max-width: 749px) {
      {% if block.settings.enable_mobile_carousel %}
        .ai-recent-jobs-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
          min-width: 85%;
          scroll-snap-align: start;
        }
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      padding-bottom: 56.25%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-recent-jobs-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 24px;
      flex-grow: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: {{ block.settings.card_text_color }};
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-route-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-route-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-route-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-route-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-route-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-left: 30px;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-route-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-details-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-chip-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      background: #f0f0f0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #555;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-chip-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
    }

    .ai-recent-jobs-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    {% if block.settings.show_trust_badges %}
      .ai-recent-jobs-badges-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-top: 16px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #008060;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-badge-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        width: 14px;
        height: 14px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.show_quote_button %}
      .ai-recent-jobs-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        margin-top: auto;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
        color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        transition: background {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
        background: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
      }
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.enable_popup %}
      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        z-index: 9999;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 300ms ease;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
        display: flex;
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        max-width: 700px;
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 90vh;
        overflow-y: auto;
        position: relative;
        transform: scale(0.9);
        transition: transform 300ms ease;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active .ai-recent-jobs-modal-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        transform: scale(1);
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-close-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        position: absolute;
        top: 16px;
        right: 16px;
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        background: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 50%;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        z-index: 10;
        transition: transform 200ms ease;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-close-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        width: 100%;
        height: 400px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: #000;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-route-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-details-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        background: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
        color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: background 300ms ease;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-modal-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
        background: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
      }
    {% endif %}

    @media (max-width: 749px) {
      .ai-recent-jobs-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
      }

      .ai-recent-jobs-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
      }

      {% if block.settings.enable_popup %}
        .ai-recent-jobs-modal-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
          height: 250px;
        }

        .ai-recent-jobs-modal-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
          padding: 24px;
        }

        .ai-recent-jobs-modal-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
          font-size: 22px;
        }
      {% endif %}
    }
  {% endstyle %}

  <recent-delivery-jobs-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-recent-jobs-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
    <div class="ai-recent-jobs-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <header class="ai-recent-jobs-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <h2 class="ai-recent-jobs-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
        <p class="ai-recent-jobs-subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheading }}</p>
      </header>

      <div class="ai-recent-jobs-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% for job in recent_jobs %}
          <article 
            class="ai-recent-jobs-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}" 
            data-job-index="{{ forloop.index0 }}"
            {% if block.settings.enable_popup %}role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="View details for {{ job.job_title.value }}"{% endif %}
          >
            <div class="ai-recent-jobs-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if job.image %}
                <img 
                  src="{{ job.image | image_url: width: 800 }}" 
                  alt="{{ job.item_type.value }} delivery from {{ job.pickup_suburb.value }} to {{ job.dropoff_suburb.value }} by Titan Express"
                  class="ai-recent-jobs-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                  width="800"
                  height="450"
                >
              {% else %}
                <div class="ai-recent-jobs-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="ai-recent-jobs-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-recent-jobs-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ job.job_title.value }}</h3>

              <div class="ai-recent-jobs-route-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-recent-jobs-route-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <span class="ai-recent-jobs-route-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2">
                      <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
                      <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <span>{{ job.pickup_suburb.value }}</span>
                </div>

                <div class="ai-recent-jobs-route-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2">
                    <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line>
                    <polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                </div>

                <div class="ai-recent-jobs-route-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <span class="ai-recent-jobs-route-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2">
                      <rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"></rect>
                      <polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"></polygon>
                      <circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle>
                      <circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"></circle>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
